<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880523-0090 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business: New Pig Corp. </HL><SO> </SO><IN> INI STK </IN><TEXT>   NEW PIG Corp., Tipton, Pa., said it is making an initial offering of 750,000 common shares at $4 each by prospectus only and directly by the company, without any underwriter. The minimum subscription, other than the exercise of preemptive rights by existing holders, is 6,250 shares, or $25,000. New Pig makes tubular products, called pig absorbent socks, that contain industrial fluids and hazardous materials. </TEXT></DOC>